{"tid":823850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運輸署：暫難估計何時能疏導東鐵綫人潮","createTime":"2018-09-17T01:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T03:31:20.000Z","uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01db243b4a0a8071044803f03e894ac73969ecdf","tid":823850,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/f26aa5e6faa9dcc6f26c39a954c45089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2Ff26aa5e6faa9dcc6f26c39a954c45089.jpg&h=81cf55ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3號風球現正懸掛，由於強颱風「山竹」吹襲後多處有塌樹瓦礫，交通嚴重受阻。港鐵表示，東鐵線大埔墟站往返上水站暫停服務，至於紅磡站往返沙田站則維持每10分鐘一班。然而，由於大圍站現正實施單軌雙行，大批乘客等待列車，逼爆月台，更一度鼓噪；也有東鐵沿線市民等候1個小時才知道沒有港鐵接駁巴士，有人抱怨等不到車，但公司又「鬼殺咁嘈」，要求政府趕快開通道路。<br />\n<br />\n據《明報》記者今早7時許在大圍站現場觀察，站內僅有1號原本往上水方向月台運作，2號原本往紅磡月台則暫停服務，故此北行和南行列車需交替進入1號月台，使月台逼滿乘客。<br />\n<br />\n另外由於大圍站在設計上，馬鞍山線轉車乘客可直接步往2號月台出市區，不需步下車站大堂再轉乘列車，故部分乘客因不知道2號月台停止服務而白白等候，直至港鐵有廣播通知後，部分乘客才得知情況，一度不滿而鼓譟。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署發言人表示，暫時估計不到何時才能疏導人潮，希望港鐵及警方可加派人手維持秩序，盼望市民盡量忍讓，聽從港鐵職員指示。發言人稱暫時署方所見大圍站較擠擁，而且市面路面亦有塌樹，呼籲市民切勿駕駛車輛出行，並留意最新交通消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537146099769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537146099769&d=Fxr%2FbJd8En57cLmWv113Cm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=675338ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537146099769&h=2a72fe6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537146099769</a>"},{"pid":"c49432576894ec76833512a8e985dcff1b2fbec6","tid":823850,"uid":117722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"而且市面路面亦有塌樹，呼籲市民切勿駕駛車輛出行，並留意最新交通消息。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚茅盾"},{"pid":"2da1f2a22084c6fe5defa0e24df9f407ae29c632","tid":823850,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:35:00.000Z","msg":"較擠擁，班官住籠屋住傻左？"},{"pid":"f6b2917de6a21d42b570bc6d22926fcbc8859da8","tid":823850,"uid":56088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"大圍卡住過唔到馬鐵線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c7d3f89c813adfefe30dcb0f3d00757fa16417","tid":823850,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c49432576894ec76833512a8e985dcff1b2fbec6","tid":823850,"uid":117722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"而且市面路面亦有塌樹，呼籲市民切勿駕駛車輛出行，並留意最新交通消息。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚茅盾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:38:10.000Z","msg":"最搞笑係有人叫人唔好屌政府，今日咁都唔可以屌政府 ？"},{"pid":"9e9e3773f828995afa7851bd53c900e3e2f7afc6","tid":823850,"uid":18879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c7d3f89c813adfefe30dcb0f3d00757fa16417","tid":823850,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c49432576894ec76833512a8e985dcff1b2fbec6","tid":823850,"uid":117722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"而且市面路面亦有塌樹，呼籲市民切勿駕駛車輛出行，並留意最新交通消息。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚茅盾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim